{
  "text": "One of the alternative treatments for H. pylori infection is probiotics, such as lactic acid bacteria and bifidobacteria. Administration of probiotics improves H. pylori eradication rates and reduces the side effects of first-line PPI-based triple therapy. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] However, the inhibitory effect of probiotics on H.",
